    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is identical to Kenjutsu: Kodachi Ryu Kaiten Kenbu, except as above, and the target must either be flat-footed or be under the effect of your Ryuusui no Ugoki. You make a Full Attack with both your weapons, gaining a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls. The target loses its Dexterity bonus to Defense only against the first attack from each weapon.</p>\n\n\n\n",
